{"tid":2278404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搶先賣IPhone2G破解版成世界新聞 先達Lo哥話當年「拎住iPhone等如拎住黃金」！","createTime":"2020-11-09T06:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T08:24:41.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"37a17b5ff42997e1d96237599632cf65f63eb7fd","tid":2278404,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310e7fc4876aeb24d109691672dc1bda2aab5279","tid":2278404,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"iPhone 12 Pro Max和iPhone 12 Mini推出在即，要知道機價市況，自然要去先達。趁着新iPhone推出，我們找來先達Lo哥等一眾先達人暢談先達事。<br />\n<br />\n先達Lo哥賣破解iPhone創歷史<br />\n<br />\n一提到先達就聯想到炒iPhone，網上亦有不少網民對炒賣負評，討論區不時出現「先達狗」這類稱呼。而最廣為網民認識的「收機佬」，就要說到每逢iPhone推出必見報的先達Lo哥。Lo哥網絡meme圖近日可能大家都見過。<br />\n<br />\n先達前身是先施百貨自用物業，1995年改建成先達商場，Lo哥在那時就入場做sales賣電話，適逢大哥大轉做摺機年代，手提電話漸見普及，過了幾年就自己開舖。當年冇iPhone獨大，要突圍而出，店家就各自搜羅獨家貨，如Mo記摺機、日本水貨機等等，各施各法。「那時做細龜（Motorola MicroTAC 7500），先達第一部我賣的，工程機來的，盒都冇，$25,000一部。」<br />\n<br />\nLo哥有知名度是有其歷史原因，可能你好憎人炒賣，但當年Lo哥搶先全球賣破解版第一代iPhone，真的是世界新聞。「iPhone第一代，2G那時，我托人由美國入了10部。那時放在店內，沒人買的，因為鎖sim卡，用不到的。」當年冇話iPhone獨大，要突圍而出就要搵獨家機款。「當時未見過有電話好似iPhone咁，可以用觸控放大縮細。」雖然香港用唔到，但都覺得有市場。<br />\n<br />\n捐窿捐罅搵貨賣，iPhone未解鎖照入，想不到殺出血路。「後來有個人找我，見我有賣iPhone，說他懂得解鎖。」這位高人...<br />\n<br />\n去到iPhone 4和4s年代，iPhone人氣去到高峰，再加上香港有首發，中國沒有，炒風一發不可收拾，足足炒足一年。那時一部iPhone 4 16GB售價$4,988，收機價可以過萬，賣一部等如免費送一部...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201109/3N3XAOHQV5BGZBDA37OZVQHN2A/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3yb32lJIQJzT2IvnK5fBJmZ42gHm-pzyegOXT8xjLdOsWVLzLg9fHsclg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201109%2F3N3XAOHQV5BGZBDA37OZVQHN2A%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3yb32lJIQJzT2IvnK5fBJmZ42gHm-pzyegOXT8xjLdOsWVLzLg9fHsclg&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=1dd2827f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201109%2F3N3XAOHQV5BGZBDA37OZVQHN2A%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3yb32lJIQJzT2IvnK5fBJmZ42gHm-pzyegOXT8xjLdOsWVLzLg9fHsclg&h=1871a7d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201109/3N3XAOHQV5BGZBDA37OZVQHN2A/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3yb32lJIQJzT2IvnK5fBJmZ42gHm-pzyegOXT8xjLdOsWVLzLg9fHsclg</a>"},{"pid":"5da6d6030492e85eb771954c844ad9b4a0a09450","tid":2278404,"uid":215755,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"自己靠犯法搵油水都周街同人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1259df5e05e126e388fc3f3097a92ab35d17db5","tid":2278404,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3nqm89f/ctp-vzntr/1528723568110538ro3or3s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3nqm89f%2Fctp-vzntr%2F1528723568110538ro3or3s.jpg&h=0f329f9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd95ef26c871e1148da47de5ca77693c9a8368b8","tid":2278404,"uid":133529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"蝕死你班仆街呀.JPG"},{"pid":"7195e3c720b3ae8ce4785e1e757a36b094014c6c","tid":2278404,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5da6d6030492e85eb771954c844ad9b4a0a09450","tid":2278404,"uid":215755,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"自己靠犯法搵油水都周街同人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20